message.body: Hey! I'm on the metro currently, but my texts might still be able to go through.
Omg you're the first person to respond
I'm at an appointment. Waiting for the lady to come in
Wait, really? You've had people who just never say anything? I don't understand why they would sign up then haha
Yes for the past 2 days
So I just gave up

That's ridiculous! Sorry about that. Today is my first day. Im also going to this conversation thing for native Spanish speakers with my mom right now, so it's kinda a big day for talking to randos for me haha
Hhhh good luck with it all
So where are you from?
I'm originally from Palestine. However, I was born and raised in North Philadelphia
You??
Oh, no kidding! When did you move? I grew up outside DC and am there til the end of the summer.
Wait you said born and raised. I'm an idiot.
Hhh its ok
So what do you do??
I'm a student. Just graduated from UVA and will be starting to earn my MSW at Boston College in September. What about you?
Ahh good luck with it all
Well I got my Associatea degree in early childhood education. I'm too lazy to go for my bachelors, so I'm working part time as a private tutor
Associates*
How old are the students you tutor?
Nice. 7 was my favorite age of childhood.
I dont recall much of my childhood.
Why do you think that is?
Could be because there wasn't much to remember
Could be because I have bad memory
Haha fair enough.
Lol. I can remember the main things, but no small details
Haha well right, that makes sense
How are you enjoying this.hot weather??
It's a bit unforgiving. And hard to decide how to dress...because buildings are so dang air conditioned sometimes! Your thoughts?
I preffer staying home most of the time. I'm Muslim so I'm covered up regardless. On top of that, I have a neurological disorder and the heat/sun are a k
iller to me. So yeah, I preffer staying indoors lol
Oh wow, yea, I'm sure! That has gotta be tough. How often do you visit Palestine?
So what do you do??
Every few years. Now, its been the longest, 6 years. I miss it
So have you done any other studys for the LCD??

Yea that's a long time to not be back. Actually I haven't! My mom just happened to forward me this email and it seemed like a good idea. My boyfriend enrolled and so we are hoping to just text through the study sometimes. Have you?
Yes. I have participated in 3 or more. The others had steady pay. I'm not really liking this one only because its based on "chance"
Like boooo!! Lol
Oh I agree! Maybe I should follow what the others are from now on though if that is where the money is!
You should bcz many of them are as simple as making a few phone calls
Ooh I like that. So what are your favorite things about/places in philly? My boyfriend's sister is moving there and doesn't know much about it.
Where is he coming in from??
Philly is home and will always have a place in my heart, but i hate it and am dying to leave
So you're pretty tired of it...
Veryyy
